      <title>特朗普枪击案嫌疑人是一名 20 岁的宾夕法尼亚州男子</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-14/suspected-gunman-in-trump-attack-is-20-year-old-pennsylvania-man</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据多家新闻媒体报道，美国联邦调查局已确认，周六在宾夕法尼亚州集会上向前总统唐纳德·特朗普开枪的枪手是 20 岁的托马斯·马修·克鲁克斯 (Thomas Matthew Crooks)。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-14/suspected-gunman-in-trump-attack-is-20-year-old-pennsylvania-man</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 14 Jul 2024 08:46:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>据法新社报道，哈马斯将退出加沙停火谈判</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-14/hamas-is-withdrawing-from-gaza-cease-fire-talks-afp-reports</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一名高级官员告诉法新社，在以色列空袭加沙地带、旨在杀死两名哈马斯高级官员的第二天，哈马斯就已退出停火谈判，此次空袭造成至少 90 人死亡，300 人受伤。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-14/hamas-is-withdrawing-from-gaza-cease-fire-talks-afp-reports</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 14 Jul 2024 08:18:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
